caption.text:
When i was little every year on December, I'd crawled up that christmas tree at home and put that big star on top of it. Hung all of the little santas, the tiny candy stick and Rudolph the red nose reindeer on every branch of the tree. As I grew older, I stopped put that big star on top of the tree and start to ignore christmas since December change into the one month that I'd never wait for. But then, just few years ago I discovered the beauty of tiny things sparkled, went on and off, the little bulbs swirling on christmas tree, tingling and wingling. And just then, I found the one thing that people called christmas spirit. I see all the happiness in people every December, I see the joy in their heart and I see the art of christmas itself. And I fell in love with christmas. 
Few months ago, everything started to went back to when christmas is not the most beautiful thing in the world. Not sure how, not sure why. But after all, that moment, the experience had taught me that no body is supposed to be happy all the time and no body could make everyone happy. You just got to let go of someone, got to dissapointed someone in your life, even if that person is the one that you love the most. So this year of christmas I learned that stop worrying to make others happy but make youself happy. Do whatever you want when you have the time, just dont waste it on the people who doesnt even appreciate you !! Merry almost christmas fellas!! #tanggal23sih #galausih #12tahunlewat #tetepgalau #merrychristmas #nggapunyagayalain

caption.text:
T R A V E L.

Yang namanya jalan-jalan, mulai dari pantai sampai gunung semuanya pasti dijabanin. Mau panas, mau dingin sekalipun di trabas aja dengan kata "kuy jalan!" Sehingga niat gue yang ingin hitam tercapai. 
Tapi sist, sebagai perempuan indonesia yang demen banget jalan pasti barang bawaannya juga banyak bgt kan, butuh sun block, lotion, ini, itu, ribet bgt kaaannnn padahal in the end you dont need all that. Jadi gue mau kasih tips packing yang amat sangat minim tapi bermanfaat. 
Packing pantai
Kalo lu travel ke pantai, jangan pernah bawa koper (ya iyalah yaa) bawa aja baju ganti satu, yang longgar banget dan panjang banget jadi pas abis maenan air pake bikini or tankini tinggal langsung pake kaos itu aja terus dijamin setelah lu sunbathing 5 menit langsung kering. Terus jangan lupa pake sandal jepit, jangan pake high heels karena bakal susah banget jalannya ya kelelep di pasir. Jangan lupa juga bawa kain-kain emesh yang bisa lu pake buat sun bathing syanthiexx. Lalu ini sebenernya barang yang paling anti gue bawa tapi penting yaituuu jeng jeng sun screen lotion, kenapa gue ngga suka? Karena kalo pake itu gue jadi ngga bisa item. Itu tips buat yang travel ke pantai. 
Next ...
Travel gunung
Kalo travel ke gunung harus punya iman yang kuat, jangan cuma sok mau keren naek gunung. Karena lu harus bawa carrier min 35lt, bawa sleeping bag buat tidur, bawa jaket yg tebel because it will freezing cold up there, bawa makanan yang cukup, jangan alay, bawa baju yang cukup juga, jangan bawa seisi lemari lu dan jangan bawa kebiasaan manja lu itu ke ataa gunung because trust me sisters, that mountain would change you big time. 
But above all that, yang paling penting dibawa saat lu travelling adalah temen-temen terbaek luuu INI PENTING! because you got to share your happiness with them. Dan .... ini adalah paket lengkap tiap gue mau travelling @palmabudiman @eufraciaindah @virginiarum

We grew up together, all I remember is that we used to play in our living room. I picked you up at the centre and defended you for years. And all the sudden, I left. I left you behind. 
For months, I learned that I couldn't leave you like that because they kept telling me that you were about to do something big to us. 
And then I remember our last birthday together, on the backyard with the cake and a candle. 
Then that big thing happened. And you became a memory. To me. To all of us. 
A good memory.
